		<h1>How do I get to the Pacific Amphitheatre?</h1>
		<iframe width="425" height="350" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" marginheight="0" marginwidth="0" src="https://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Orange+County+Fairgrounds,+Fair+Drive,+Costa+Mesa,+CA&amp;aq=0&amp;oq=orange+county+fair&amp;sll=37.269174,-119.306607&amp;sspn=13.90489,19.753418&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=Orange+County+Fairgrounds,+Fair+Drive,+Costa+Mesa,+CA&amp;t=m&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;cid=2296049349719343994&amp;ll=33.666633,-117.899042&amp;output=embed"></iframe><br /><small><a href="https://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Orange+County+Fairgrounds,+Fair+Drive,+Costa+Mesa,+CA&amp;aq=0&amp;oq=orange+county+fair&amp;sll=37.269174,-119.306607&amp;sspn=13.90489,19.753418&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=Orange+County+Fairgrounds,+Fair+Drive,+Costa+Mesa,+CA&amp;t=m&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;cid=2296049349719343994&amp;ll=33.666633,-117.899042" style="color:#0000FF;text-align:left">View Larger Map</a></small>
		<h2>Parking</h2>
		<p>Follow the signs to Fair Dr. and enter the fairgrounds through either the Main Gate or Gate 2. Parking is free in Lots B and C, located directly inside those gates.</p>
